item.title: CVE-2019-11212|2024-09-16T19:41:44.955Z -- tibco%20software%20inc. -- tibco%20mdm
item.description: The MDM server component of TIBCO Software Inc's TIBCO MDM contains multiple vulnerabilities that theoretically allow an authenticated user with specific roles to perform cross-site scripting (XSS) attacks. This issue affects TIBCO Software Inc.'s TIBCO MDM version 9.0.1 and prior versions; version 9.1.0.
